data.description: 24 hour notice required for showing    ***NEW PRICE***  Welcome to this stunning home nestled in the highly sought-after Hickory Ridge neighborhood, ideally located in the 33813 zip code in great school zones. Situated on a peaceful cul-de-sac, this meticulously maintained property boasts a range of exceptional features that make it a true gem. Here are some of the highlights: Roof and hot water heater both replaced in 2022 and the air conditioner was upgraded in 2017, and there's a solar attic fan for increased efficiency. This home also features newer hurricane impact, tinted windows.  An inviting open concept featuring 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, living and dining rooms, a large family room with a fireplace and a big BONUS room (341 sq ft) The kitchen features newer appliances, lots of counter space and a pass thru to family and bonus rooms. Other features include newer luxury vinyl flooring and the inside laundry room is equipped with built-in shelves.   A large screened patio overlooks your private back yard---filled with multiple fruit trees (grapefruit, blood orange, 3X lemon, loquat, lime,  bananas and blackberry vines in the yard.) Add to this a  large Smithbuilt shed with garage door in the backyard for great additional  storage and wood fencing encloses the entire back yard.  This home backs up to PROTECTED  land, ensuring privacy and no rear neighbors.  Convenient location in South Lakeland with easy access to shopping, medical and major highways...yet tucked away and private !
